title: Titanic's last lunch menu, from Money Boat, goes for $88,000
text:
> Entertainment Titanic's last lunch menu, from Money Boat, goes for $88,000 FILE - This undated file photo provided by Lion Heart Autographs shows the Titanic’s last lunch menu. The menu — saved by a passenger who climbed aboard the so-called “Money Boat” before the ocean liner went down — was sold at an auction Wednesday, Sept. 30, 2015.
